overview: The top shelf is reserved for the best of the best, and this movie features 12 of SCORE’s best girls with the best top shelves. All of them are covergirls and award-winners. All of them have big, natural racks. Nine of these scenes are unique, have never been released on DVD. There’s no one single star of this movie. They’re all stars! Hitomi, Alexya, Venera, Karla James, Valory Irene, Christy Marks, Sha Rizel, Micky Bells, Arianna Sinn, Leanne Crow, Merilyn Sakova and Karina Hart.
title: Top Shelf
